      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean and retains a nice shine, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scratch on the rear bumper consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is very tidy with minimal wear on the upholstery, and all electronic features, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully functional. Mechanically, the car is sound, starts reliably, and has a consistent service history, making it an excellent choice for someone looking for a dependable vehicle that still looks great on the road.",
