    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she is honestly such a joy to drive. She\u2019s been really well-taken care of, runs super smoothly, and is ready for a new home! Perfect for daily commutes or weekend adventures. Come take her for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how she handles! \u2728",
