    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six power plant. This unit exhibits crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and maintains optimal variable valve timing through a serviced double-VANOS system. The chassis remains composed with a reinforced rear subframe and upgraded polyurethane bushings, ensuring the factory limited-slip differential translates torque effectively to the tarmac. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides tactile engagement with precise gate selection. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain remains robust and high-revving. A driver-centric example for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
